 mod support and DLC.If you are into hunting IRL and are looking for a decent game, well then this is probably going to be for you anyway.... But if you have a passing interest in this concept, then wait for another dev to release something similar or else at least wait for a sale as you will need the ATV DLC.Hopefully another dev comes along and builds on the Hunter COTW concept without the greed and lack of mod support.This is a nice game thats been well made and i would like to recommend but just feel like i cant given the greedy DLC move and lack of mod support."
