w, with more too come. Given the flaws, it still remeains one of the best Hunting games out there.Devs------------------------------------So far they have been pushing big updates weekly, also with a few hot fixes inbetween. They are well aware of the broken game they gave us, and they intend to fix it. With bugs getting squashed weekly, this game will get better than it already is and I will gladly support it. The Devs are active in the Forums at times and they listen too our feedback.Conclusion-----------------------------------Overall this is a Hunting game that still lacks features and equipment to call it a ""complete"" game, but at its core it still remains one of the better Hunting games out there and I gladly support it.6.5/10"
