 look around every time I made a noise. Such natural animations and behaviour. Love the fur variations.- I had a feeling of being rewarded with a beautiful hunt despite never finding a deer corpse that I shot. How? These devs are witches.- Maps. Those current two I can explore are ENORMOUS and beautifly done in every detail.Cons:- Maybe I am biased but could a shot deer die a bit faster? No? ok10/10What I'd love to see:- Tons of more maps! Current amazing maps make me crave for more biomes like Asian forests with musk deer or barbary deer in Africa. I'd spend any $ to get more maps and never stop staring at beautiful landscapes.You guys got me hooked on your stuff and you got a customer for life. Hopefully."
