 15 minutes while simulatenously trying to stay hidden and keep my noise down. Maybe I'm just being too critical as this is a video game, and not real life, but it'd be helpful.Again the tracking is the BIGGEST issue in this game. Once that gets sorted, then it would be an absolutely perfect hunting sim.Overall right now 8.2/10 With an update to the tracking; if you're wanting a hunting sim, 10/10Buy this game now if you want a close to perfection hunting sim."
