 game would not have ""micro transactions"" but later added vital parts of the game ""tents and blinds"" as a paid for DLC and this can be seen as a bit of a kick in the balls for those that paid for a game that should have been all inclusive, for the ATV DLC I can see this as not being completely needed but wanted so it should have been added as a paid for addon."
