,Recommended,518790,32373858,Posted: 12 June,all,|OS| Kerkenbush,"The best hunting game out there currently. That being said there is no competition in this genre so it's still not exactly a stellar game... Yet. The graphics are beautiful and the lighting and sound are awesome. The controls are simple and the hud makes sense though it isn't visually impressive or unique. The gameplay is a lot of fun when it works yet, there are some serious animal AI issues and various other bugs (some gamebreaking) still in existence. All animals will return to you if you remain hidden and call them back. It doesn't matter if you just shot 500 rounds and the rest of the herd is scattered about the area as corpses. They will return always and forever. There are ""rare"" legendary animals which always spawn in the same area at the same time of day. After a while you start to realize there is no real challenge. If these issues get ironed out this could be a truly amazing game. There seems to be a patch about every few weeks so the potential is still there. As of right now it's only a slightly above average hunting game.6/10When everything works murder can be so rewarding."
