,Recommended,518790,31407817,Posted: 27 April,all,coRpSE,"I started playing this a few days ago and I have to say that it is a bit addictive. Of course, with every game there is bugs and downfalls that will need ot be addressed. But even with the bugs and downfalls, there are many great things about this game. This game has become my latest game that I stream and enjoy streaming it every chance I can.The things I do like about the game thus far is the AI seems to be more realistic than many other games. Another thing I like about the game is the landscape, it is beautiful and flows great. The colors and the whole weather/day & night is great. But even with that, there are a few gripes about this game that really irks me.The things in this game that bugs me is a few and I needed to separate them into their own groups. Mind you that this list is in no way game breaking or anything to stop me from enjoying the game, just things that I found to be a bit annoying or wrong.Economy System- The economy is really messed up. I cant believe a Fellow Deer call cost the same amount as a rifle, or a compound bow. I just feel that someone went through and just slapped some values to the items and put zero thought into it. The cost of most things seems to be really high compared to how much you earn in game. I like to see that get adjusted a bit.Core Function DLC- Core function of the game being placed as a paid DLC. Though I don't mind them having paid DLC, I do believe that should be left to content that does not require everyone to have it, even if they don't pay for it. For example, skins. They can make some good money off selling skins for rifles, flags, banners, ect..., and which also does not require people that have not bought the item to have it downloaded and installed on their hard drives.Character Movement- The only issues I have had with that is when moving up and down hills. The character does not seem to be able to jump very well. I believe the jump needs to be raised a bit and the distance a little more. The characters need to have their feet picked up a bit more. The characters almost shuffle their feet rather than walking.Communication- Seems that the developers don't communicate very well, and really don't have a good system available for proper bug reporting. The steam forums is not a good platform. Hell, even setting up a reddit would be better.There are also a few bugs which have been posted, it's just a matter of them fixing it and when. But overall, I do recommend this game and I will continue to play it and enjoy it."
