.  The description of the game says it's based on 7 years of the Classic game's experience.  Well that must be in the hunting features and not UI creation.  Provided they fix the UI issues, I really have no major complaints.  The hunting experience has been really good so far in my play.  I've not tested the Multi-player group hunt stuff yet, but so far, I've enjoyed it, as have my kids.  I just wish they'd get the UI working properly, particularly when it comes to buying things, using the menus, etc..."
